Good design is [[appropriate]] to its [[context]].

== Global designs ==

What of designs such as the [[mobile phone]], which are used globally in almost every human context - do they disprove the need for appropriate technology and appropriate design? 

Not at all - the mobile phone is still essentially appropriate to [[human scale]] and essential human needs and desires, i.e. [[communication]] and [[convenience]].

